{"pageProps":{"note":{"id":"359kuswvs74ufyh92re9s8q","title":"Openvpn3","desc":"","updated":1662646271224,"created":1662644652415,"custom":{},"fname":"linux.applications.openvpn3","type":"note","vault":{"fsPath":".","selfContained":true,"name":"docs"},"contentHash":"eabfb5e2fd4dcc4c4f703a142ac7c1a7","links":[{"type":"wiki","from":{"fname":"linux.applications.openvpn3","id":"359kuswvs74ufyh92re9s8q","vaultName":"docs"},"value":"kyber","position":{"start":{"line":4,"column":22,"offset":34},"end":{"line":4,"column":31,"offset":43},"indent":[]},"xvault":false,"sameFile":false,"to":{"fname":"kyber"}}],"anchors":{"openvpn3":{"type":"header","text":"OpenVPN3","value":"openvpn3","line":8,"column":0,"depth":1},"install":{"type":"header","text":"Install","value":"install","line":12,"column":0,"depth":2},"simple-start":{"type":"header","text":"Simple start","value":"simple-start","line":31,"column":0,"depth":2},"commands":{"type":"header","text":"Commands","value":"commands","line":37,"column":0,"depth":2}},"children":[],"parent":"phh329wgik4nmti5o5ny6po","data":{}},"body":"<h1 id=\"openvpn3\">Openvpn3<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#openvpn3\"></a></h1>\n<h1 id=\"openvpn3-1\">OpenVPN3<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#openvpn3-1\"></a></h1>\n<ul>\n<li>used to access the <a title=\"Private\" href=\"https://wiki.dendron.so/notes/hfyvYGJZQiUwQaaxQO27q.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"private\">kyber (Private)</a> dev environment</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"install\">Install<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#install\"></a></h2>\n<blockquote>\n<p><a href=\"https://community.openvpn.net/openvpn/wiki/OpenVPN3Linux?__cf_chl_jschl_tk__=8242c8ca4f6aec5ca5596d45ae0208a68ad5edc0-1616667818-0-ATzy_Y6a7l84X7ALx0iFoIW9DWpak-xag5ue93rFf57I8zEVYY353f0q-pZUnQsRxCJGtYQAz-ov3JCP_qZrVMJDgJzZaSbZPPvDn4EOLDRyqSfIWY8QIWGAVBd-BHYirKKgZ7FPkASeg8gQwH1tPEJ58Zb3sZeNTP6N9xUjM4fZAkHHElPlQzI8mLUevwCnAID9jQpzeyshpp2rOP6avmnIPk1_nj0obWnB53LrT75Wy0v-E9mouaUhkRulzkK3k41ZCDLzXpMzvLpsikjb97ZK1jXq7P4UoGfJjgcvAN_i4KIjCnqAOC_UReoEGZni_uTkCSuvLq_0dOD_qzgy5OYu3Wml3Q3MlPDqEG-rNM3N\">https://community.openvpn.net/openvpn/wiki/OpenVPN3Linux?__cf_chl_jschl_tk__=8242c8ca4f6aec5ca5596d45ae0208a68ad5edc0-1616667818-0-ATzy_Y6a7l84X7ALx0iFoIW9DWpak-xag5ue93rFf57I8zEVYY353f0q-pZUnQsRxCJGtYQAz-ov3JCP_qZrVMJDgJzZaSbZPPvDn4EOLDRyqSfIWY8QIWGAVBd-BHYirKKgZ7FPkASeg8gQwH1tPEJ58Zb3sZeNTP6N9xUjM4fZAkHHElPlQzI8mLUevwCnAID9jQpzeyshpp2rOP6avmnIPk1_nj0obWnB53LrT75Wy0v-E9mouaUhkRulzkK3k41ZCDLzXpMzvLpsikjb97ZK1jXq7P4UoGfJjgcvAN_i4KIjCnqAOC_UReoEGZni_uTkCSuvLq_0dOD_qzgy5OYu3Wml3Q3MlPDqEG-rNM3N</a>\n<a href=\"https://github.com/OpenVPN/openvpn3-linux/issues/113\">https://github.com/OpenVPN/openvpn3-linux/issues/113</a></p>\n</blockquote>\n<ul>\n<li>Ubuntu\n<ul>\n<li>https transport: <code>sudo apt install apt-transport-https</code> </li>\n<li>add source key\n<pre><code>sudo wget https://swupdate.openvpn.net/repos/openvpn-repo-pkg-key.pub\nsudo apt-key add openvpn-repo-pkg-key.pub\n</code></pre>\n</li>\n<li>set up source\n<pre><code>sudo bash -c 'curl -fsSL https://swupdate.openvpn.net/community/openvpn3/repos/openvpn3-focal.list > /etc/apt/sources.list.d/openvpn3.list'\n</code></pre>\n<ul>\n<li>focal: Ubuntu 20.04</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>update &#x26; install: <code>sudo apt update &#x26;&#x26; sudo apt install openvpn3</code></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"simple-start\">Simple start<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#simple-start\"></a></h2>\n<pre><code>openvpn3 session-start --config ${MY_CONFIGURATION_FILE}\n</code></pre>\n<h2 id=\"commands\">Commands<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#commands\"></a></h2>\n<ul>\n<li>show sessions\n<pre><code>openvpn3 session-list\n</code></pre>\n</li>\n<li>disconnet\n<pre><code>openvpn3 session-manage --config ${MY_CONFIGURATION_FILE} --disconnect\n</code></pre>\n</li>\n</ul>","noteIndex":{"id":"xfkxbponh0sohobo6pual15","title":"Root","desc":"","updated":1668137379975,"created":1663481872547,"custom":{"nav_order":0,"permalink":"/"},"fname":"root","type":"note","vault":{"fsPath":".","selfContained":true,"name":"docs"},"contentHash":"cb44915142ec96bef8f764f3dc90389e","links":[],"anchors":{"welcome-to-my-page":{"type":"header","text":"Welcome to my page","value":"welcome-to-my-page","line":7,"column":0,"depth":1},"contacts":{"type":"header","text":"Contacts","value":"contacts","line":12,"column":0,"depth":2},"dendron":{"type":"header","text":"Dendron","value":"dendron","line":18,"column":0,"depth":2}},"children":["u5a2e2vvfn3x7k0shuvmb1b","qw8y69zxn8wr7tzz4gtcrrv","q7qw45jglqwmynary64q67c","6wjqcjgkrpeqtmzb1o8o1q8","3ervbn5we7t8v2l2vwtx847","4qi2z0z9fquupbd651xausx","sencgim78q74o1zuyvy1vz7","ue4oml1si982t3mmbthyxi9","zrogwjgtze8ne5joqpz8ty9","oesia0lbzh03fsoy124ck0k","el3p9zjue6h3b6zsl9oejkt","t5grkmcwvu4nl43igsj4gxz"],"parent":null,"data":{},"body":"# Welcome to my page\n\n- This is a place where I write my knowledge in both Vietnamese and English.\n- Please feel free to correct me if there is anything not right.\n\n## Contacts\n\n- [Github](https://github.com/thanhpp)\n- [Discord](https://discord.gg/ugNRjFNqjp)\n- [LinkedIn](https://www.linkedin.com/in/thanhpp/)\n\n## Dendron\n\n- [Home Page](https://wiki.dendron.so/)"},"collectionChildren":null,"customHeadContent":null,"config":{"version":5,"dev":{"enablePreviewV2":true,"enableSelfContainedVaults":true},"commands":{"lookup":{"note":{"selectionMode":"extract","confirmVaultOnCreate":true,"vaultSelectionModeOnCreate":"alwaysPrompt","leaveTrace":false,"bubbleUpCreateNew":true,"fuzzThreshold":0.2}},"randomNote":{},"insertNoteLink":{"aliasMode":"none","enableMultiSelect":false},"insertNoteIndex":{"enableMarker":false},"copyNoteLink":{"aliasMode":"title"},"templateHierarchy":"template"},"workspace":{"vaults":[{"fsPath":".","selfContained":true,"name":"docs"}],"journal":{"dailyDomain":"daily","name":"journal","dateFormat":"y.MM.